%% =========================
%% User Flow
%% =========================
U --> WEB

WEB --> CHAT

CHAT --> API

API --> ORCH

ORCH --> RAG

RAG --> VECTOR

VECTOR --> PROMPT

PROMPT --> GEMINI

GEMINI --> RESPONSE

RESPONSE --> CHAT

CHAT --> U

%% Knowledge Sync
SITE -. Incremental Content Sync .-> VECTOR

%% Database Options
VECTOR -. Lightweight .-> QDRANT

VECTOR -. Enterprise .-> PG

PG --> DASH

